name: LED "OPEN" Sign
description:
Call customer attention to your business and let them know that your are open day or night with this bright LED open sign! This high visibility LED sign has bright white, red, and blue LED lights with three selectable modes: static, tracer, and Vegas. You can even adjust the speed where the special modes flash!

LED lights are brighter than traditional neon lights and can be seen in direct sunlight, so it's easy for customers to see when you're ready for business throughout the day and night. Plus, LED lights consume far less energy than traditional neon lights! Its lightweight construction makes it easy to mount to any vertical surface. Two 30" long chains enable the sign to be hung from the ceiling, and a 10' power cord ensures flexibility in placement.

Perfect for your pizza shop, bar, or game room, when the sign is hanging and the lights are in motion, customers won't be able to miss your business! The oval LED open sign measures 21"W x 13"H x 2"D. Requires a 110V electrical connection

name: Scrolling Color LED Sign
description: The TruColorII LED display is the ultimate in color display technology. The TruColorII LED display has built-in entertaining and attention getting features such as "Trivia in Motion" and the ability to receive satellite updates with an optional receiver to display stock quotes, sports scores and news which makes it ideal for welcoming and entertaining guests at lobbies, sports bars and more. With the included infrared wireless remote, the TruColorII LED display may be programmed in a matter of minutes. The TruColorII LED display is also easily programmable via PC through direct connection! It comes with a serial plug to connect to your PC. If your computer does not have a serial port, serial to USB converters are readily available at local electronics stores. The overall dimensions of this LED sign are 28" W x 1.875" D x 4.5" H.

name: LED "COFFEE" Sign
description:
This super bright, 22" x 13" rectangular LED sign features the word COFFEE in bold, decorative red letters. A stylish blue coffee cup and saucer design precedes the text, with lighted white "steam" rising from the cup.

Three display modes, including steady on, flashing, and crawling, are controlled by an on-board switch box. Save your business money with this LED sign, which offers an economical alternative to traditional high-voltage, breakable neon lights.

name: LED "PIZZA" Sign
description: Tempt customers to a deliciously saucy slice of pie at your pizza shop or pizzeria with this ultra bright LED pizza sign! The LED pizza sign features a multi-colored piping hot pizza design, and the word "PIZZA" in bright green lettering. LED lights are brighter than traditional neon lights and can be seen in direct sunlight so your message can be viewed both day and night. Its lightweight construction makes it easy to mount to any vertical surface. The oval pizza sign measures 22 3/4"W x 14"H. Includes chain for hanging sign.
